data.description: Nestled in the neighborhood of Rockvale Meadows, this home offers 2,354 sq. ft of living space on over half an acre. This residence exudes charm with dark hardwood floors, high ceilings, natural light, beautiful trim work, crown molding, and an upgraded kitchen with stainless steel appliances. Main floor offers a separate sitting area or playroom. Formal dining room is the perfect space to host your holidays. High ceilings in living room as well as tiled fireplace and floating shelves make it perfect for gathering with family and friends. Master suite is a retreat with tray ceiling, double vanities, tiled walk-in shower, and a separate soaking tub complete with a walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms as well as large bonus room offer versatility for guests, a home office, or media room for cozy nights in. New Roof in 2022! 1% closing cost credit of loan amount with Suggested Lender! Make this home yours today!
